        593.05
      ],
      "text": "onderneming.",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        70.82,
        633.76,
        188.77,
        642.76
      ],
      "text": "Doelstelling / resultaat",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        70.82,
        650.2,
        328.97,
        659.2
      ],
      "text": "De voortgang van de re-integratieactiviteiten is in beeld:",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        88.82,
        682.96,
        355.53,
        691.96
      ],
      "text": "- Hoe is het starten als zelfstandige tot nu toe verlopen?",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
